text: The Greens – The Green Alternative (, shortened to GRÜNE) is an Austrian political party. Its leader is Werner Kogler and it is founded 1993. The party is a member of the European Green Party and its ideology is Center-Left. The main ideology is green politics that aims to create an ecologically sustainable society. == Other websites == * Category:1993 establishments in Europe Category:1990s establishments in Austria Category:Green political parties Category:Political parties in Austria
